vernac_cmds: Theorem Empty_set_zero : forall X:Ensemble U, Union U (Empty_set U) X = X.
Theorem Empty_set_zero_right : forall X:Ensemble U, Union U X (Empty_set U) = X.
Theorem Empty_set_zero' : forall x:U, Add U (Empty_set U) x = Singleton U x.
unfold Add at 1; auto using Empty_set_zero with sets.
Lemma less_than_empty : forall X:Ensemble U, Included U X (Empty_set U) -> X = Empty_set U.
Theorem Union_commutative : forall A B:Ensemble U, Union U A B = Union U B A.
Theorem Union_associative : forall A B C:Ensemble U, Union U (Union U A B) C = Union U A (Union U B C).
Theorem Union_idempotent : forall A:Ensemble U, Union U A A = A.
Lemma Union_absorbs : forall A B:Ensemble U, Included U B A -> Union U A B = A.
Theorem Couple_as_union : forall x y:U, Union U (Singleton U x) (Singleton U y) = Couple U x y.
intros x y; apply Extensionality_Ensembles; split; red.
intros x0 H'; elim H'; (intros x1 H'0; elim H'0; auto with sets).
intros x0 H'; elim H'; auto with sets.
Theorem Triple_as_union : forall x y z:U, Union U (Union U (Singleton U x) (Singleton U y)) (Singleton U z) = Triple U x y z.
intros x y z; apply Extensionality_Ensembles; split; red.
intros x1 H'0; elim H'0; (intros x2 H'1; elim H'1; auto with sets).
intros x1 H'0; elim H'0; auto with sets.
intros x0 H'; elim H'; auto with sets.
Theorem Triple_as_Couple : forall x y:U, Couple U x y = Triple U x x y.
Theorem Triple_as_Couple_Singleton : forall x y z:U, Triple U x y z = Union U (Couple U x y) (Singleton U z).
rewrite <- (Couple_as_union x y); auto with sets.
Theorem Intersection_commutative : forall A B:Ensemble U, Intersection U A B = Intersection U B A.
split; red; intros x H'; elim H'; auto with sets.
Theorem Distributivity : forall A B C:Ensemble U, Intersection U A (Union U B C) = Union U (Intersection U A B) (Intersection U A C).
intros x0 H'0 H'1; generalize H'0.
elim H'; intros x0 H'0; elim H'0; auto with sets.
Lemma Distributivity_l : forall (A B C : Ensemble U), Intersection U (Union U A B) C = Union U (Intersection U A C) (Intersection U B C).
Theorem Distributivity' : forall A B C:Ensemble U, Union U A (Intersection U B C) = Intersection U (Union U A B) (Union U A C).
intros x0 H'0; elim H'0; auto with sets.
intros x0 H'0; elim H'0; auto with sets.
intros x1 H'1 H'2; try exact H'2.
Theorem Union_add : forall (A B:Ensemble U) (x:U), Add U (Union U A B) x = Union U A (Add U B x).
unfold Add; auto using Union_associative with sets.
Theorem Non_disjoint_union : forall (X:Ensemble U) (x:U), In U X x -> Add U X x = X.
intros X x H'; unfold Add.
intros x0 H'0; elim H'0; auto with sets.
intros t H'1; elim H'1; auto with sets.
Theorem Non_disjoint_union' : forall (X:Ensemble U) (x:U), ~ In U X x -> Subtract U X x = X.
intros X x H'; unfold Subtract.
intros x0 H'0; elim H'0; auto with sets.
intros x0 H'0; apply Setminus_intro; auto with sets.
lapply (Singleton_inv U x x0); auto with sets.
intro H'4; apply H'; rewrite H'4; auto with sets.
Lemma singlx : forall x y:U, In U (Add U (Empty_set U) x) y -> x = y.
intro x; rewrite (Empty_set_zero' x); auto with sets.
Lemma incl_add : forall (A B:Ensemble U) (x:U), Included U A B -> Included U (Add U A x) (Add U B x).
intros A B x H'; red; auto with sets.
lapply (Add_inv U A x x0); auto with sets.
intro H'1; elim H'1; [ intro H'2; clear H'1 | intro H'2; rewrite <- H'2; clear H'1 ]; auto with sets.
Lemma incl_add_x : forall (A B:Ensemble U) (x:U), ~ In U A x -> Included U (Add U A x) (Add U B x) -> Included U A B.
intros A B x H' H'0 x0 H'1.
intro H'2; lapply (Add_inv U B x x0); auto with sets.
intro H'3; elim H'3; [ intro H'4; try exact H'4; clear H'3 | intro H'4; clear H'3 ].
absurd (In U A x0); auto with sets.
Lemma Add_commutative : forall (A:Ensemble U) (x y:U), Add U (Add U A x) y = Add U (Add U A y) x.
rewrite (Union_associative A (Singleton U x) (Singleton U y)).
rewrite <- (Union_associative A (Singleton U y) (Singleton U x)); auto with sets.
Lemma Add_commutative' : forall (A:Ensemble U) (x y z:U), Add U (Add U (Add U A x) y) z = Add U (Add U (Add U A z) x) y.
rewrite (Add_commutative (Add U A x) y z).
rewrite (Add_commutative A x z); auto with sets.
Lemma Add_distributes : forall (A B:Ensemble U) (x y:U), Included U B A -> Add U (Add U A x) y = Union U (Add U A x) (Add U B y).
intros A B x y H'; try assumption.
rewrite <- (Union_add (Add U A x) B y).
Lemma setcover_intro : forall (U:Type) (A x y:Ensemble U), Strict_Included U x y -> ~ (exists z : _, Strict_Included U x z /\ Strict_Included U z y) -> covers (Ensemble U) (Power_set_PO U A) y x.
intros; apply Definition_of_covers; auto with sets.
Lemma Disjoint_Intersection: forall A s1 s2, Disjoint A s1 s2 -> Intersection A s1 s2 = Empty_set A.
Lemma Intersection_Empty_set_l: forall A s, Intersection A (Empty_set A) s = Empty_set A.
Lemma Intersection_Empty_set_r: forall A s, Intersection A s (Empty_set A) = Empty_set A.
Lemma Seminus_Empty_set_l: forall A s, Setminus A (Empty_set A) s = Empty_set A.
Lemma Seminus_Empty_set_r: forall A s, Setminus A s (Empty_set A) = s.
Lemma Setminus_Union_l: forall A s1 s2 s3, Setminus A (Union A s1 s2) s3 = Union A (Setminus A s1 s3) (Setminus A s2 s3).
constructor; inversion H; inversion H0; intuition.
Lemma Setminus_Union_r: forall A s1 s2 s3, Setminus A s1 (Union A s2 s3) = Setminus A (Setminus A s1 s2) s3.
Lemma Setminus_Disjoint_noop: forall A s1 s2, Intersection A s1 s2 = Empty_set A -> Setminus A s1 s2 = s1.
Lemma Setminus_Included_empty: forall A s1 s2, Included A s1 s2 -> Setminus A s1 s2 = Empty_set A.
Hint Resolve Empty_set_zero Empty_set_zero' Union_associative Union_add singlx incl_add: sets.
